      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――密着取材、最終日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Close Coverage‚ Final Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "スリクスのセンターは私よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm ⅢX's center.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2000001192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "真ん中に立つのは当然でしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's natural for me to stand in the middle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そんなの、ただの思考停止じゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's just thoughtless.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3666667859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "曲を大事にしない人は、センターに相応しくないでーす",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Someone who doesn't value the song isn't suitable for center~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……え？　franとkanaが喧嘩しているのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh? Even though fran and kana are fighting‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9666667859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに平然としていていいのかって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "is it okay for me to be so calm?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.3469964181,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私達は固い絆で結ばれていると信じていますが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I believe we're bound by strong bonds‚ but",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.5000001192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "なあなあの馴れ合いがいいとも思っていません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "we don't think that overly agreeable relationships are good either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お互い、忌憚のない意見をぶつけ合いますし――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We clash with each other's frank opinions‚ and--",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3000001192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "時にはあんな風に、喧嘩になることだってありますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "sometimes it becomes a fight like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "……本当に、たまにですけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Really‚ just occasionally though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.5333334525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "二人とも、そのくらいにしておきなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both of you‚ leave it at that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4000001192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "今回は……そうね、私もkanaと同意見よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This time… yes‚ I agree with kana too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ただ、今までの私達のイメージを崩したくないから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I don't want to break our image up until now‚ so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.7666667859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、2コーラス目ではfranがこっちに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ in the second chorus‚ fran should go over here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（な、なんとか誤魔化せた……か？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（D-did we somehow manage to cover it up…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.2333334525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
