      "text": "（良かった、どうなることかと思った……！！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Thank goodness‚ I wondered what would happen…!!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
